Comment: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:06.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:06.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에도토피아를 향한 여행을 계속하는 무사시는 쿠사리가마를 사용하는 바이켄과 만나 대전했다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:06.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi had a match against Baiken, the user of {\i1}kusarigama{\i0}, during the trip to Edotopia.
Comment: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:13.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:13.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,처음 보는 쿠사리가마의 위력의 대단함에 한결같던 무사시도 쩔쩔, 고전을 면치 못한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:13.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,In front of the might of kusarigama that he saw for the first time, Musashi was flustered and had a hard fight.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:22.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:22.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 우정이 트었다. 그리고 에도토피아의 무예 대회에서 재회를 단단히 약속하고 떠났다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:22.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,But after all, a new friendship has born. Musashi has promised to meet him again in the martial arts competition, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:27.65,TitleEP,ko,0,0,70,,악의 한조, 살며시 다가오오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:27.65,TitleEP,en,0,0,60,,Evil Hanzō Creeps
Comment: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,한조 님, 기다리셨습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting, Lord Hanzō.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.07,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,100,,한조
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.07,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,100,,Hanzō
Comment: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래, 마중 수고했다, 젠조.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. I appreciate you for greeting me, Zenzō.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼, 예의 물건은?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, where is the thing?
Comment: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예, 이 안에 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes, it is inside here.
Comment: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is it.
Comment: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇군. 훌륭한 등급이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see. They seem to be perfect.
Comment: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:27.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:27.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻게 해서라도 밖으로 알려지지 않게 해라.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:27.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not let any information about this place leak.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:27.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:27.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:27.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:32.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:32.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것만 있으면 천하는 나, 한조의 것.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:32.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,With this, the world is in my hands.
Comment: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:49.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:49.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 쯤 무사시는 코지로를 마음에 두고 있으면서도, 애도 코테츠를 허리에 차고 쭉 에도토피아를 향해 가고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:49.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, having Kojirō in mind, Musashi was heading to Edotopia, carrying Kotetsu, his beloved swords, on his waist.
Comment: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저건 코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,That must be Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔가 소생에게 볼 일이?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you have anything to say to me?
Comment: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:11.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:11.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 아니, 그게, 다른 사람이었소. 실례했소.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:11.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, no, uh, that is, I was looking for a different person-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Excuse me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐야, 얘?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's up with this guy?
Comment: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠조인가.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is it Zenzō?
Comment: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-예.\N-말해라.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Speak.
Comment: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:59.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:59.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,며칠 전, 호조인 도장에 경찰 장관 주베가 나타났다 합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:59.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,A few days ago, it is told that Jūbē, the police chief, stopped by at Hōzōin Dōjō.
Comment: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,ジュウベエが？おのれ。。。諸国の動静を探るは奴にはあらず。
Comment: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:07.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:07.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주베가? 그 놈... 제국의 동세를 정탐하는 역이 아닐 터.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:07.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jūbē? That bastard... He is not supposed to be a spy investigating across the state.
Comment: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내탐꾼인 내 임무를 넘보고 손톱끝으로 다룰 생각을 하다니.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,How dare he tries to take over my role?
Comment: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:17.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:17.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 이런 때, 그런 곳에 주베가 나타났다는 것은 설마 그 금광...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:17.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,But it is possible that Jūbē appeared in that place because of the gold mine...
Comment: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당황하지 마라. 실수는 없다. 그쪽은...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't be flustered. There is no mistake. And for you...
Comment: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who is there?!
Comment: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,수상한 놈이다! 잡아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Spies! Get them!
Comment: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이대로는 함께 잡힌다. 너라도 달아나라!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're going to be caught like this. Run away by yourself!
Comment: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럴 수는 없다! 뭔 생각인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I shall not! Why would you say that?
Comment: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:48.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:48.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우리가 함께 잡히면 한조의 음모를 누가...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:48.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,If we get caught together, who will expose Hanzō's plot?
Comment: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자. 빨리 이걸 주베 님께!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take this to Jūbē right away!
Comment: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Something's over there!
Comment: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,넌 그쪽을 찾아봐라! 난 저 넘어를 보겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,You go look that way! I'll check over that side.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내겐 신경쓰지 마라. 서둘러라!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Forget about me. Hurry!
Comment: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,찾았다!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Found him!
Comment: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안하다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Appreciated.
Comment: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Comment: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:27.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:27.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 쯤 코지로는 무사시를 전혀 신경쓰지 않고 쭉 에도토피아를 향하고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:27.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Kojirō was heading to Edotopia, and Musashi was nowhere to be found in his thoughts.
Comment: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 일인가, 대체?! 정신 차려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,What happened? Wake up!
Comment: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주, 주베 님께...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bring this to Jūbē...
Comment: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 괜찮나! 어이!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you alright? Hey!
Comment: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비둘기?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Pigeons?
Comment: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주베에게?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,To Jūbē?
Comment: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭘 가지고 웅성대오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you all talking about-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죽은 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is it dead?
Comment: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 움직이네.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's not moving.
Comment: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-비둘기!\N-응, 상처를 입고 저 나무 아래에 떨어져 있었어.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,-A pigeon!\N-Yeah, it was under that tree injured.
Comment: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,상처를? 그럼 빨리 돕지 않으면 불쌍하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Injured? We must help that pitiful thing in that case-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,하오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}dasu{\i0}, you say?
Comment: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말을 해도 우리는 카라쿠리 새는 어떻게 못 해.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, we can't do anything about a karakuri bird.
Comment: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 그런 거라면 내게 맡기시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can leave that to me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얼마 줄 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,How much are you going to pay us-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얼마라니, 주운 거 아니오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,How much? Didn't you say you picked this up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 그래라! 그럼 어딘가에 버리러 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it! Then let's go throw it away at somewhere else!
Comment: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쩨쩨하긴!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,So stingy!
Comment: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-가자.\N-아, 멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N-Hey, stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거참, 최근 아이들은 방심할 수가 없소...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Man, kids nowadays are so sneaky-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 이 정도면 만족하오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here! Are you satisfied-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-이제 산 것이오!\N-이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,-You bought it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!\N-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것 참...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Man.
Comment: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 어쨌든 한번 보겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me take a look-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,와, 대단한 상처이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's a big wound-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오, 이것은?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,What-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,참 비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,How cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내게 무슨 원한이 있는 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,What do you have against me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나중에 꼭 치료해 줄 테니까 여기 있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll come back later to treat you, so stay here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 뭔 일이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, what's going on-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구시오! 왜 날 노리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who are you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?! Why are you after me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}무사시가 왜 닌자들에게...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are ninjas chasing Musashi?
Comment: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:31.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:31.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,설마 조금 전 닌자를 무사시가 죽이기라도 한 것인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:31.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it possible that Musashi killed that other ninja just before?
Comment: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,발 빠른 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,What swift rat!
Comment: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-잡아라!\N-어이!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Catch him!\N-Right!
Comment: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,끈질긴 놈들이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,What persistent bastards-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어째 내가 이런 상황에 처하게 됐소...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did I wrong to get in this situation-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,놈들, 설마 이걸...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are they possibly looking for this...?
Comment: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}무사시 놈, 어떻게든 추격자를 따돌린 모양이구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems that Musashi has managed to get away from pursuers.
Comment: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}But yet...
Comment: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋소, 이제 괜찮을 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right, you're going to be fine-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다시 날 수 있게 될 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,You'll be able to fly again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 이것도 돌려주는 게 좋겠소...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Maybe I should better return this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait!
Comment: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너, 너는!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yo- you are!
Comment: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 짓이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 비둘기의 주인하고 죽은 자하고 상관있는 듯 하구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that the owner of this dove and the dead are somehow related.
Comment: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쨌든 이것이 주베와 관계가 있을 듯 하다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anyway, this seems to be has something to do with Jūbē.
Comment: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주베 씨하고?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,With Jūbē?
Comment: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,This...
Comment: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩌면 무언가의 부호.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Possibly, a code of something.
Comment: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 글자를 숨긴 밀서일지도.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Or a secret message using steganography.
Comment: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,밀서이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,A secret message-dasu?
Comment: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다. 읽어보면 네가 몹시 노려진 이유도 알게 될 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. We should know the reason you were chased by reading this.
Comment: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라, 이것은!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,글자이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a character-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이, 이건 대체!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇군, 이런 장치였군!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,So I see how this device works.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:25.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:25.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 잘 되어 있다. 비치는 것은 여기에 적혀 있던 글자다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:25.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's pretty well done. The characters written inside are getting projected.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왠지 읽혀지지 않소...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,I can't read for some reason-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내가 읽겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will read.
Comment: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:38.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:38.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것은 바늘구멍 사진기를 응용한 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:38.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is an application of the mechanism behind a pinhole camera.
Comment: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:45.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:45.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,핀홀 카메라라고 불려, 렌즈 대신 작은 구멍을 이용한, 말하자면 카메라의 고선조격이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:45.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's as if an ancestor of the modern cameras, using a small hole instead of a lens.
Comment: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,"두 개의 얼굴을 가진 악당, 한조의 정체를 여기에 적는다."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,"Hanzō, a villain with two faces, shall be exposed here."
Comment: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,한조? 누구이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō? Who is it?
Comment: 0,0:11:53.75,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,伊賀忍軍頭領 / 公儀隠密
Comment: 0,0:11:53.75,0:12:00.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:12:00.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나도 잘은 모르지만 이하(伊賀) 닌자의 수장으로써 제너럴 이에야스 막부의 밀정이라고 들었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:12:00.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Not that I know well, but I heard that he is the head of the Iga ninjas, working as an official spy under General Ieyasu.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 날 쫒은 건 그 밀정이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then was that spy chasing me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니. 아닌 것 같다. 한번 봐라.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,No. I don't think so. Take a look for yourself.
Comment: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:15.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:15.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,"이 남자, 막부의 밀정으로써 지팡구국의 치안을 지키는 장군이면서 실은 뒤에서 다이묘 간 싸움을 붙여
Comment: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 세상의 치안을 어지럽히는 일을 이어왔습니다."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:12.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,"This man is a general who maintains public peace and order as an official spy,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,"but yet he makes daimyos fight against each other from behind,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,"continuing his practice of stirring up trouble."
Comment: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:25.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:25.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,"게다가 이만큼이나 신고하지 않고 각지의 금광을 소유하는 것은 분명히 막부를 전복시키려는 것."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:25.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,"Moreover, owning many gold mines across the state without reporting can only mean to overthrow the shogunate."
Comment: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:30.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:30.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,"자신이 지팡구국의 막후 조종자로써 군림하고자 한다는 증거입니다."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:30.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,"It is the proof that he is scheming to reign over Jipangu State as the shadow shogun."
Comment: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:36.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:36.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,"다음은 금광의 위치입니다. 주베 님의 결단을 바랍니다."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:36.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,"Following is the location of gold mine. Waiting for the decision from Jūbē."
Comment: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,번거로운 놈이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's one troublesome guy-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:49.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:49.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,한조의 마의 손이 다가온다. 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:49.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō's evil hands are approaching. Wait for the stormy latter half!
Comment: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사정을 알았지만 말려들고 싶지는 않다.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,While I got the situation, I do not want to be involved.
Comment: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 말이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you saying-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알아채지 못했나, 무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Didn't you get it, Musashi?!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:12.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:12.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:12.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,생명을 소홀히 여기지 마라! 다시 만나자!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not spend your life for nothing! See you again!
Comment: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오, 코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:27.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:27.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,따라오지 마라! 둘로 나뉘어 위기를 모면해라! 다른 길로 돌아가라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:27.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not follow me! Divide up to two and escape this situation! Change your path!
Comment: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말을 해도 혼자 달아날 수는 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, I cannot run away by myself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 내가 건너로 가겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I'll go that way instead!
Comment: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wh- what the-?!
Comment: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우리하고는 어떤 관계도 없다. 비켜라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,We have nothing to do with that. Move away!
Comment: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐요?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,What the-?!
Comment: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 것에는 당하지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't fall for that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh no-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:26.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:26.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장! 이렇게 됐다면 익히든 태우든 원하는 대로 하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:26.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dammit! Cook, throw into a fire, or do whatever you want-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벌써 저런다. 왜 녀석은 단세포인 거냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,He already gave up. What simpleton he is!
Comment: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거기까지다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go!
Comment: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼을 내려놓아라! 안 놓으면 생명은 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Put down the sword! Or he's as good as dead!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 원하는 대로 하는 건 싫소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Okay, I wouldn't like if they do whatever they want-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나하고는 상관없는 일이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with this!
Comment: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일단, 이 녀석은 무엇도 가지고 있지 않다. 죽여봤자 소용없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,First, that guy does not have anything. Even if you kill, you won't get a thing!
Comment: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무, 무슨 무책임한 소리를!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,How irresponsible he is!
Comment: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:58.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:58.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐, 너희들 직성 풀릴 때까지 알아보면 알게 되겠지.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:58.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Well, you might understand if you investigate as much as you want.
Comment: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라! 달아나는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop right there! You shall not run away!
Comment: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이, 이건!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wh- what the...
Comment: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 코지로 놈, 달아났소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn... Kojirō ran away-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없지. 어쨌든 퇴각이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's no use. Retreating for now.
Comment: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 녀석이라도 있으면 어떻게든 되겠지. 충분히 알아볼 테니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,At least we'd be able to find something out from this guy. We'll find out in plenty.
Comment: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이거 놓으시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Untie me!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,활기찬 사내자식이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a lively boy.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:38.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:38.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너는!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:38.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,You!
Comment: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:48.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:48.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이하 닌자 군단 수장, 한조! 그보다도 그렇게 날뛰어도 괜찮을까, 꼬맹아.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:48.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Head of Iga Ninja Force, Hanzō! But first, would you be okay to act violently, you brat?
Comment: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:03.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:03.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네 발 아래에는 지뢰가 깔려 있다. 균형을 잃으면 바로 떨어지겠지.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:03.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,There are mines under your feet. If you lose balance, you'll fall right away.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 밀서는 어디 있나!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Tell me where the secret message is!
Comment: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 밀서 따위 가지고 있지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't have any secret message-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,하지만 비둘기에는 없었다. 어디에 숨겼나!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,But it wasn't in the pigeon. Where did you hide the message at?
Comment: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모르는 것은 모르는 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know what I don't know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:18.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:18.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋다. 어디까지 그 고집이 갈지 보여줘 보아라.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:18.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Alright then. Let's see when your stubbornness goes away.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-네가 떨어지는 동안 그 장치는 자연을 따른다.\N-비겁하오! 난 아무것도 모르오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,-As you slowly fall, that device will follow law of nature.\N-You're cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I know nothing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살고 싶다면 그 전에 숨긴 곳을 밝혀라.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you want to live, you shall reveal the location you hid the message.
Comment: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:42.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:42.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 걸 하면 밀서는 찾을 수 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:42.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you keep doing this, you won't be able to find the secret message-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,상관없다. 산 증인은 하나 더 있으니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. There is another living witness.
Comment: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자. 그 동안 한가로이 기다리고나 있을까.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, let us wait with leisure meanwhile.
Comment: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:57.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:57.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-잘 보고 있어라.\N-살려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:57.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Keep an eye on him.\N-Help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 내가 이런 꼴에 처해야 하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why must I be in this situation-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래! 코지로다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's it! Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇소! 코지로가 달아난 탓이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! It's all because Kojirō ran away!
Comment: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로 개새끼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō's an idiot!
Comment: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고통스럽소, 비겁자!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm suffering, you coward!
Comment: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,더 말하면 안 살려준다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,One more word and I'm not saving you.
Comment: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로! 어느 순간에...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō! When did you...
Comment: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:29.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:29.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,연기 속에서 갈아입었다. 너 같은 녀석이라도 없으면 허전하니 말이지.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:29.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,I changed my clothes in the smoke. Even if it's you, I would miss you should you cease to be.
Comment: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 달아나자!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Let's run away!
Comment: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,탈출 성공! 빨리 이 집에서 나가오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Escape success! Let's hurry and get out of this mansion-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멍청하긴. 적이 있는 곳에서는 내 칼만으로는 무리다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Idiot. When there are enemies everywhere, my sword alone isn't enough.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네 칼도 찾아야 한다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,We must find your sword too!
Comment: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오, 이건?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is this?
Comment: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,가짜 맹장지다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,A fake sliding screen.
Comment: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 코테츠!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,My kotetsu!
Comment: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,묘하군... 추적자의 기미가 없다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Strange... There are no sign of chasers.
Comment: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:23.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:23.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,분명 한조 놈이 그새 자버린 바람에 깨닫지 못하는 것일 테오.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:23.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō must have fallen asleep, not realizing that we escaped-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 괜찮겠지만... 어쨌든 서두르자!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I hope so, but let's hurry up for now.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:33.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:33.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멍청한 놈. 그저 달아나게 두었다 생각하나.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:33.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Idiots. You shall not simply run away.
Comment: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,밀서의 소재를 알게 될 쯤에 천천히 죽여 주겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,When I get to know where the secret message is, I'll kill you slowly.
Comment: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:43.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:43.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐? 그 밀서, 에도토피아의 주베 님께 전달한다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:43.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying that you're going to deliver that secret message to Jūbē in Edotopia?
Comment: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇소. 한조같은 극악한 자는 용서할 수 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. An atrocious villain like Hanzō is unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 말이지,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still...
Comment: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 잠깐!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Comment: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:56.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:56.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋소.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:56.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good.
Comment: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것으로 한조 일당도 끝장이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,With this, Hanzō's gang will meet its end-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아! 멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Comment: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너, 너는!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,You- you must be...!
Comment: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 받았다. 가라!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's ours now. Go!
Comment: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 너무 재빠르오!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, they are too quick-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석들, 우리를 쫒아왔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Those guys followed us!
Comment: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,밀서를 빼앗겼소!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,They took the message-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:46.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:46.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내버려둬라! 이 이상 둘러싸이는 것은 사양이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:46.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Forget it! I refuse to be involved more than this!
Comment: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말을 해도!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even if you say so...
Comment: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,해냈소.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,We did it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩌면 좋소?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,What should we do-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱히 방법이 있을까보냐! 별 방법이 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Like I know! We just run!
Comment: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,끝장이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll finish you!
Comment: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:45.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:45.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:45.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,돌려주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take it back-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 애송이들이...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,You damned brats...
Comment: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 원한은 꼭 갚아주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will have revenge on you!
Comment: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,즉각적으로 적의 무기를 이용하는 것은 너 치고는 훌륭했다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thinking to use your enemy's weapon in a nick of time is praiseworthy even for you.
Comment: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼, 다시 갈라질까.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then let's separate from now on.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나하고의 승부가 남아있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,You still have a match against me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너하고 같이 있으면 제대로 되는 게 없으니 말이지.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,You know, with you, nothing goes alright.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,게다가, 나도 이런 편리한 것을 가지고 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,And also, I also have some convenient stuff.
Comment: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:49.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:49.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안녕이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:49.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,바보 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Comment: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라, 배가 고파서 똑바로 설 수가 없소...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh, I'm too hungry to stand up straight-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:13.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:13.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이렇게, 한조의 마의 손은 피해갔지만 그 무서운 음모를 밝히는 밀서를 잃어버렸다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:13.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,In this way, he managed to evade the evil hands of Hanzō, but he lost the secret message revealing his fearsome plot.
Comment: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:23.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:23.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배가 고파 힘이 들어, 무사는 먹지 않아도 긍지많은 높다지만 갈 길은 먼 무사시였다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:23.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,He was too tired and hungry. A starved swordsman still has high spirits, but Musashi wasn't quite there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.99,SongED1,ED1!Lyric01,0,0,0,,カラのポケットに　ツキが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:48.25,SongED1,ED1!Lyric02,0,0,0,,飛び込むことも　あるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.62,SongED1,ED1!Lyric03,0,0,0,,おっきな声で　笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:53.25,SongED1,ED1!Lyric04,0,0,0,,あしたには　朝が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:58.59,SongED1,ED1!Lyric05,0,0,0,,無くすものなんか　何もないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:02.18,SongED1,ED1!Lyric06,0,0,0,,やっちゃえ！イケイケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.60,SongED1,ED1!Lyric07,0,0,0,,手ぶらは　強いぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:14.69,SongED1,ED1!Lyric08,0,0,0,,てなもんだ　のーてんきに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:22.74,SongED1,ED1!Lyric09,0,0,0,,人生　てなもんさ　チャンスが　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:27.45,SongED1,ED1!Lyric10,0,0,0,,しっぽを振って　追ってくるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:38.38,SongED1,ED1!Lyric11,0,0,0,,てなもんだ　のーてんきに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:46.85,SongED1,ED1!Lyric12,0,0,0,,未来も　てなもんさ　あしたが　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:52.69,SongED1,ED1!Lyric13,0,0,0,,両手ひろげて　笑ってるぜ
Comment: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,飲み放題食い放題
Comment: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:08.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:08.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마음껏 먹고 마셨소. 게다가 용돈까지 벌 수 있어서
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:08.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've ate and drink as much as I wanted-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Moreover, because I could earn money,
Comment: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 카츠조 일가를 돕게 되었소만,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,I decided to help Katsuzō family-{\i1}dasu{\i0},
Comment: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:15.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:15.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 공짜보다 비싼 것은 없다고 다들 그러오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:15.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,but as everyone says, there's no such thing as a free lunch-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:20.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:20.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 무슨, 형제의 약속을 맺은 이시마츠 씨가 있는 지로치오 일가하고 싸우게 되고 말았소.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:20.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,A twist of fate? I have to fight against Jirochiō family where Ishimatsu, who promised with me to be brothers, is in-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:24.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:24.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 사내 이시마츠, 우정이 지다
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:24.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! A Man Ishimatsu, Friendship Falls-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:27.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:27.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 우정으로 우시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:27.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Cry by the stormy friendship-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
